Package koopa.core.targets

Class HoldingTarget

java.lang.Object
koopa.core.targets.HoldingTarget
All Implemented Interfaces:
Target
public class HoldingTarget extends Object implements Target
This is a Target which will refrain from forwarding its Data to another target until instructed to do so 'via shiftAllToNextTarget()).

In addition to the delay, you can also retract the data which was pushed up to the point of the last shiftAllToNextTarget().
